Package joelib2.data Description

These classes are the chemical heart of JOELib. A lot of the chemical expert knownledge is available in this package:

  • define atom types
  • understand and define chemical aromaticity
  • protonation state of atoms
  • initialization of partial charge calculation
  • periodic table knownledge, e.g. know simply how many exterior electrons a atom can have
